67  uint16_t len)

177 int32_t lsm6dsox_xl_full_scale_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx,
178  lsm6dsox_fs_xl_t val)
179 {
180  lsm6dsox_ctrl1_xl_t reg;
181  int32_t ret;
182 
183  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
184  if (ret == 0) {
185  reg.fs_xl = (uint8_t) val;
186  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
187  }
188  return ret;
189 }
190 
198 int32_t lsm6dsox_xl_full_scale_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_fs_xl_t *val)
199 {
200  lsm6dsox_ctrl1_xl_t reg;
201  int32_t ret;
202 
203  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
204  switch (reg.fs_xl) {
205  case LSM6DSOX_2g:
206  *val = LSM6DSOX_2g;
207  break;
208  case LSM6DSOX_16g:
209  *val = LSM6DSOX_16g;
210  break;
211  case LSM6DSOX_4g:
212  *val = LSM6DSOX_4g;
213  break;
214  case LSM6DSOX_8g:
215  *val = LSM6DSOX_8g;
216  break;
217  default:
218  *val = LSM6DSOX_2g;
219  break;
220  }
221 
222  return ret;
223 }

232 int32_t lsm6dsox_xl_data_rate_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_odr_xl_t val)
233 {
234  lsm6dsox_odr_xl_t odr_xl = val;
235  lsm6dsox_emb_fsm_enable_t fsm_enable;
236  lsm6dsox_fsm_odr_t fsm_odr;
237  uint8_t mlc_enable;
238  lsm6dsox_mlc_odr_t mlc_odr;
239  lsm6dsox_ctrl1_xl_t reg;
240  int32_t ret;
241 
242  /* Check the Finite State Machine data rate constraints */
243  ret = lsm6dsox_fsm_enable_get(ctx, &fsm_enable);
244  if (ret == 0) {
245  if ( (fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm1_en |
246  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm2_en |
247  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm3_en |
248  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm4_en |
249  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm5_en |
250  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm6_en |
251  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm7_en |
252  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_a.fsm8_en |
253  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm9_en |
254  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm10_en |
255  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm11_en |
256  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm12_en |
257  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm13_en |
258  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm14_en |
259  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm15_en |
260  fsm_enable.fsm_enable_b.fsm16_en ) == PROPERTY_ENABLE ){
261 
262  ret = lsm6dsox_fsm_data_rate_get(ctx, &fsm_odr);
263  if (ret == 0) {
264  switch (fsm_odr) {
265  case LSM6DSOX_ODR_FSM_12Hz5:
266 
267  if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF){
268  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5;
269 
270  } else {
271  odr_xl = val;
272  }
273  break;
274  case LSM6DSOX_ODR_FSM_26Hz:
275 
276  if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF){
277  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz;
278 
279  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5){
280  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz;
281 
282  } else {
283  odr_xl = val;
284  }
285  break;
286  case LSM6DSOX_ODR_FSM_52Hz:
287 
288  if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF){
289  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
290 
291  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5){
292  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
293 
294  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz){
295  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
296 
297  } else {
298  odr_xl = val;
299  }
300  break;
301  case LSM6DSOX_ODR_FSM_104Hz:
302 
303  if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF){
304  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
305 
306  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5){
307  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
308 
309  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz){
310  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
311 
312  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz){
313  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
314 
315  } else {
316  odr_xl = val;
317  }
318  break;
319  default:
320  odr_xl = val;
321  break;
322  }
323  }
324  }
325  }
326 
327  /* Check the Machine Learning Core data rate constraints */
328  mlc_enable = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
329  if (ret == 0) {
330  ret = lsm6dsox_mlc_get(ctx, &mlc_enable);
331  if ( mlc_enable == PROPERTY_ENABLE ){
332 
333  ret = lsm6dsox_mlc_data_rate_get(ctx, &mlc_odr);
334  if (ret == 0) {
335  switch (mlc_odr) {
336  case LSM6DSOX_ODR_PRGS_12Hz5:
337 
338  if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF){
339  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5;
340 
341  } else {
342  odr_xl = val;
343  }
344  break;
345  case LSM6DSOX_ODR_PRGS_26Hz:
346  if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF){
347  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz;
348 
349  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5){
350  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz;
351 
352  } else {
353  odr_xl = val;
354  }
355  break;
356  case LSM6DSOX_ODR_PRGS_52Hz:
357 
358  if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF){
359  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
360 
361  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5){
362  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
363 
364  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz){
365  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
366 
367  } else {
368  odr_xl = val;
369  }
370  break;
371  case LSM6DSOX_ODR_PRGS_104Hz:
372  if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF){
373  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
374 
375  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5){
376  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
377 
378  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz){
379  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
380 
381  } else if (val == LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz){
382  odr_xl = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
383 
384  } else {
385  odr_xl = val;
386  }
387  break;
388  default:
389  odr_xl = val;
390  break;
391  }
392  }
393  }
394  }
395  if (ret == 0) {
396  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
397  }
398  if (ret == 0) {
399  reg.odr_xl = (uint8_t) odr_xl;
400  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
401  }
402  return ret;
403 }

412 int32_t lsm6dsox_xl_data_rate_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_odr_xl_t *val)
413 {
414  lsm6dsox_ctrl1_xl_t reg;
415  int32_t ret;
416 
417  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL1_XL, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
418 
419  switch (reg.odr_xl) {
420  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF:
421  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF;
422  break;
423  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5:
424  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_12Hz5;
425  break;
426  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz:
427  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_26Hz;
428  break;
429  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz:
430  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_52Hz;
431  break;
432  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz:
433  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_104Hz;
434  break;
435  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_208Hz:
436  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_208Hz;
437  break;
438  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_417Hz:
439  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_417Hz;
440  break;
441  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_833Hz:
442  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_833Hz;
443  break;
444  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_1667Hz:
445  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_1667Hz;
446  break;
447  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_3333Hz:
448  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_3333Hz;
449  break;
450  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_6667Hz:
451  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_6667Hz;
452  break;
453  case LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_6Hz5:
454  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_6Hz5;
455  break;
456  default:
457  *val = LSM6DSOX_XL_ODR_OFF;
458  break;
459  }
460  return ret;
461 }

692  }
693  if (ret == 0) {
694  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL2_G, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
695  }
696  if (ret == 0) {
697  reg.odr_g = (uint8_t) odr_gy;
698  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL2_G, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
699  }
700 
701  return ret;
702 }

856 int32_t lsm6dsox_xl_power_mode_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx,
857  lsm6dsox_xl_hm_mode_t val)
858 {
859  lsm6dsox_ctrl5_c_t ctrl5_c;
860  lsm6dsox_ctrl6_c_t ctrl6_c;
861  int32_t ret;
862 
863  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t*) &ctrl5_c, 1);
864  if (ret == 0) {
865  ctrl5_c.xl_ulp_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x02U) >> 1;
866  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t*) &ctrl5_c, 1);
867  }
868  if (ret == 0) {
869  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL6_C, (uint8_t*) &ctrl6_c, 1);
870  }
871  if (ret == 0) {
872  ctrl6_c.xl_hm_mode = (uint8_t)val & 0x01U;
873  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL6_C, (uint8_t*) &ctrl6_c, 1);
874  }
875  return ret;
876 }
877 
885 int32_t lsm6dsox_xl_power_mode_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx,
886  lsm6dsox_xl_hm_mode_t *val)
887 {
888  lsm6dsox_ctrl5_c_t ctrl5_c;
889  lsm6dsox_ctrl6_c_t ctrl6_c;
890  int32_t ret;
891 
892  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL5_C, (uint8_t*) &ctrl5_c, 1);
893  if (ret == 0) {
894  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL6_C, (uint8_t*) &ctrl6_c, 1);
895  switch ( (ctrl5_c.xl_ulp_en << 1) | ctrl6_c.xl_hm_mode) {
896  case LSM6DSOX_HIGH_PERFORMANCE_MD:
897  *val = LSM6DSOX_HIGH_PERFORMANCE_MD;
898  break;
899  case LSM6DSOX_LOW_NORMAL_POWER_MD:
900  *val = LSM6DSOX_LOW_NORMAL_POWER_MD;
901  break;
902  case LSM6DSOX_ULTRA_LOW_POWER_MD:
903  *val = LSM6DSOX_ULTRA_LOW_POWER_MD;
904  break;
905  default:
906  *val = LSM6DSOX_HIGH_PERFORMANCE_MD;
907  break;
908  }
909  }
910  return ret;
911 }

971 int32_t lsm6dsox_all_sources_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx,
972  lsm6dsox_all_sources_t *val)
973 {
974  int32_t ret;
975 
976  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_SRC,
977  (uint8_t*)&val->all_int_src, 1);
978  if (ret == 0) {
979  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_WAKE_UP_SRC,
980  (uint8_t*)&val->wake_up_src, 1);
981  }
982  if (ret == 0) {
983  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_TAP_SRC,
984  (uint8_t*)&val->tap_src, 1);
985  }
986  if (ret == 0) {
987  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_D6D_SRC,
988  (uint8_t*)&val->d6d_src, 1);
989  }
990  if (ret == 0) {
991  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_STATUS_REG,
992  (uint8_t*)&val->status_reg, 1);
993  }
994  if (ret == 0) {
995 
996  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
997  }
998  if (ret == 0) {
999  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_STATUS,
1000  (uint8_t*)&val->emb_func_status, 1);
1001  }
1002  if (ret == 0) {
1003  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_STATUS_A,
1004  (uint8_t*)&val->fsm_status_a, 1);
1005  }
1006  if (ret == 0) {
1007  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_STATUS_B,
1008  (uint8_t*)&val->fsm_status_b, 1);
1009  }
1010  if (ret == 0) {
1011  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MLC_STATUS,
1012  (uint8_t*)&val->mlc_status, 1);
1013  }
1014  if (ret == 0) {
1015  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
1016  }
1017 
1018  return ret;
1019 }

1715 int32_t lsm6dsox_mem_bank_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_reg_access_t *val)
1716 {

1718  int32_t ret;
1719 
1720  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FUNC_CFG_ACCESS, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
1721  switch (reg.reg_access) {

1723  *val = LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK;
1724  break;

1726  *val = LSM6DSOX_SENSOR_HUB_BANK;
1727  break;
1728  case LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK:
1729  *val = LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK;

1733  break;

1737 
1746 int32_t lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t address,
1747  uint8_t *val)
1748 {
1749  lsm6dsox_page_rw_t page_rw;
1750  lsm6dsox_page_sel_t page_sel;
1751  lsm6dsox_page_address_t page_address;
1752  int32_t ret;
1753 
1754  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
1755 
1756  if (ret == 0) {
1757  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1758  }
1759  if (ret == 0) {
1760  page_rw.page_rw = 0x02; /* page_write enable */
1761  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1762  }
1763  if (ret == 0) {
1764  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t*) &page_sel, 1);
1765  }
1766 
1767  if (ret == 0) {
1768  page_sel.page_sel = ((uint8_t)(address >> 8) & 0x0FU);
1769  page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
1770  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t*) &page_sel, 1);
1771  }
1772  if (ret == 0) {
1773  page_address.page_addr = (uint8_t)address & 0xFFU;
1774  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_ADDRESS,
1775  (uint8_t*)&page_address, 1);
1776  }
1777  if (ret == 0) {
1778  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_VALUE, val, 1);
1779  }
1780  if (ret == 0) {
1781  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1782  }
1783  if (ret == 0) {
1784  page_rw.page_rw = 0x00; /* page_write disable */
1785  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1786  }
1787  if (ret == 0) {
1788 
1789  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
1790  }
1791  return ret;
1792 }
1793 
1803 int32_t lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t address,
1804  uint8_t *buf, uint8_t len)
1805 {
1806  lsm6dsox_page_rw_t page_rw;
1807  lsm6dsox_page_sel_t page_sel;
1808  lsm6dsox_page_address_t page_address;
1809  int32_t ret;
1810  uint8_t msb, lsb;
1811  uint8_t i ;
1812 
1813  msb = ((uint8_t)(address >> 8) & 0x0FU);
1814  lsb = (uint8_t)address & 0xFFU;
1815 
1816  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
1817  if (ret == 0) {
1818 
1819  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1820  }
1821  if (ret == 0) {
1822  page_rw.page_rw = 0x02; /* page_write enable*/
1823  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1824  }
1825  if (ret == 0) {
1826  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t*) &page_sel, 1);
1827  }
1828  if (ret == 0) {
1829  page_sel.page_sel = msb;
1830  page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
1831  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t*) &page_sel, 1);
1832  }
1833  if (ret == 0) {
1834  page_address.page_addr = lsb;
1835  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_ADDRESS,
1836  (uint8_t*)&page_address, 1);
1837  }
1838 
1839  if (ret == 0) {
1840 
1841  for (i = 0; ( (i < len) && (ret == 0) ); i++)
1842  {
1843  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_VALUE, &buf[i], 1);
1844 
1845  /* Check if page wrap */
1846  if ( (lsb == 0x00U) && (ret == 0) ) {
1847  lsb++;
1848  msb++;
1849  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t*)&page_sel, 1);
1850  if (ret == 0) {
1851  page_sel.page_sel = msb;
1852  page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
1853  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL,
1854  (uint8_t*)&page_sel, 1);
1855  }
1856  }
1857  }
1858  page_sel.page_sel = 0;
1859  page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
1860  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t*) &page_sel, 1);
1861  }
1862  if (ret == 0) {
1863 
1864  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1865  }
1866  if (ret == 0) {
1867  page_rw.page_rw = 0x00; /* page_write disable */
1868  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1869  }
1870 
1871  if (ret == 0) {
1872 
1873  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
1874  }
1875  return ret;
1876 }
1877 
1886 int32_t lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t address,
1887  uint8_t *val)
1888 {
1889  lsm6dsox_page_rw_t page_rw;
1890  lsm6dsox_page_sel_t page_sel;
1891  lsm6dsox_page_address_t page_address;
1892  int32_t ret;
1893 
1894  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
1895  if (ret == 0) {
1896 
1897  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1898  }
1899  if (ret == 0) {
1900  page_rw.page_rw = 0x01; /* page_read enable*/
1901  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1902  }
1903  if (ret == 0) {
1904 
1905  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t*) &page_sel, 1);
1906  }
1907  if (ret == 0) {
1908  page_sel.page_sel = ((uint8_t)(address >> 8) & 0x0FU);
1909  page_sel.not_used_01 = 1;
1910  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_SEL, (uint8_t*) &page_sel, 1);
1911  }
1912  if (ret == 0) {
1913  page_address.page_addr = (uint8_t)address & 0x00FFU;
1914  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_ADDRESS,
1915  (uint8_t*)&page_address, 1);
1916  }
1917  if (ret == 0) {
1918 
1919  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_VALUE, val, 2);
1920  }
1921  if (ret == 0) {
1922  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1923  }
1924  if (ret == 0) {
1925  page_rw.page_rw = 0x00; /* page_read disable */
1926  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
1927  }
1928  if (ret == 0) {
1929  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
1930  }
1931 
1932  return ret;
1933 }

2753 int32_t lsm6dsox_ois_mode_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_spi2_read_en_t val)
2754 {

2767  (uint8_t*)&func_cfg_access, 1);
2768  }

2771  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FUNC_CFG_ACCESS,
2772  (uint8_t*)&func_cfg_access, 1);
2773  }
2774  return ret;

3835 int32_t lsm6dsox_i3c_disable_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_i3c_disable_t val)
3836 {
3837  lsm6dsox_i3c_bus_avb_t i3c_bus_avb;
3838  lsm6dsox_ctrl9_xl_t ctrl9_xl;
3839  int32_t ret;
3840 
3841  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL9_XL, (uint8_t*)&ctrl9_xl, 1);
3842  if (ret == 0) {
3843  ctrl9_xl.i3c_disable = ((uint8_t)val & 0x80U) >> 7;
3844  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL9_XL, (uint8_t*)&ctrl9_xl, 1);
3845  }
3846  if (ret == 0) {
3847 
3848  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
3849  (uint8_t*)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
3850  }
3851  if (ret == 0) {
3852  i3c_bus_avb.i3c_bus_avb_sel = (uint8_t)val & 0x03U;
3853  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
3854  (uint8_t*)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
3855  }
3856 
3857  return ret;
3858 }

3868 int32_t lsm6dsox_i3c_disable_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_i3c_disable_t *val)
3869 {
3870  lsm6dsox_ctrl9_xl_t ctrl9_xl;
3871  lsm6dsox_i3c_bus_avb_t i3c_bus_avb;
3872  int32_t ret;
3873 
3874  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_CTRL9_XL, (uint8_t*)&ctrl9_xl, 1);
3875  if (ret == 0) {
3876  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_I3C_BUS_AVB,
3877  (uint8_t*)&i3c_bus_avb, 1);
3878 
3879  switch ((ctrl9_xl.i3c_disable << 7) | i3c_bus_avb.i3c_bus_avb_sel) {
3880  case LSM6DSOX_I3C_DISABLE:
3881  *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_DISABLE;
3882  break;
3883  case LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_50us:
3884  *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_50us;
3885  break;
3886  case LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_2us:
3887  *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_2us;
3888  break;
3889  case LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_1ms:
3890  *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_1ms;
3891  break;
3892  case LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_25ms:
3893  *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_ENABLE_T_25ms;
3894  break;
3895  default:
3896  *val = LSM6DSOX_I3C_DISABLE;
3897  break;
3898  }
3899  }
3900  return ret;
3901 }

4286 int32_t lsm6dsox_pin_mode_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_pp_od_t *val)

4290  int32_t ret;

4296  }

4309  *val = LSM6DSOX_INT1_NOPULL_DOWN_INT2_OPEN_DRAIN;
4310  break;
4311  default:
4312  *val = LSM6DSOX_PUSH_PULL;
4313  break;
4314  }
4315  return ret;
4316 }

4413 int32_t lsm6dsox_int_notification_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_lir_t val)
4414 {
4415  lsm6dsox_tap_cfg0_t tap_cfg0;
4416  lsm6dsox_page_rw_t page_rw;
4417  int32_t ret;
4418 
4419  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_TAP_CFG0, (uint8_t*) &tap_cfg0, 1);
4420  if (ret == 0) {
4421  tap_cfg0.lir = (uint8_t)val & 0x01U;
4422  tap_cfg0.int_clr_on_read = (uint8_t)val & 0x01U;
4423  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_TAP_CFG0, (uint8_t*) &tap_cfg0, 1);
4424  }
4425  if (ret == 0) {
4426 
4427  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
4428  }
4429  if (ret == 0) {
4430  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
4431  }
4432  if (ret == 0) {
4433  page_rw.emb_func_lir = ((uint8_t)val & 0x02U) >> 1;
4434  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
4435  }
4436  if (ret == 0) {
4437  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
4438  }
4439 
4440  return ret;
4441 }

4450 int32_t lsm6dsox_int_notification_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_lir_t *val)
4451 {
4452  lsm6dsox_tap_cfg0_t tap_cfg0;
4453  lsm6dsox_page_rw_t page_rw;
4454  int32_t ret;
4455 
4456 
4457  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_TAP_CFG0, (uint8_t*) &tap_cfg0, 1);
4458  if (ret == 0) {
4459 
4460  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
4461  }
4462  if (ret == 0) {
4463  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
4464  }
4465  if (ret == 0) {
4466  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
4467  }
4468  if (ret == 0) {
4469  switch ((page_rw.emb_func_lir << 1) | tap_cfg0.lir) {
4470  case LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_PULSED:
4471  *val = LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_PULSED;
4472  break;
4473  case LSM6DSOX_BASE_LATCHED_EMB_PULSED:
4474  *val = LSM6DSOX_BASE_LATCHED_EMB_PULSED;
4475  break;
4476  case LSM6DSOX_BASE_PULSED_EMB_LATCHED:
4477  *val = LSM6DSOX_BASE_PULSED_EMB_LATCHED;
4478  break;
4479  case LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_LATCHED:
4480  *val = LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_LATCHED;
4481  break;
4482  default:
4483  *val = LSM6DSOX_ALL_INT_PULSED;
4484  break;
4485  }
4486  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
4487  }
4488  if (ret == 0) {
4489  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PAGE_RW, (uint8_t*) &page_rw, 1);
4490  }
4491  if (ret == 0) {
4492  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
4493  }
4494 
4495  return ret;
4496 }

5580 int32_t lsm6dsox_ff_dur_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, uint8_t val)
5581 {
5582  lsm6dsox_wake_up_dur_t wake_up_dur;
5583  lsm6dsox_free_fall_t free_fall;
5584  int32_t ret;
5585 
5586  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_WAKE_UP_DUR, (uint8_t*)&wake_up_dur, 1);
5587  if (ret == 0) {
5588  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FREE_FALL, (uint8_t*)&free_fall, 1);
5589  }
5590  if (ret == 0) {
5591  wake_up_dur.ff_dur = ((uint8_t)val & 0x20U) >> 5;
5592  free_fall.ff_dur = (uint8_t)val & 0x1FU;
5593  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_WAKE_UP_DUR,
5594  (uint8_t*)&wake_up_dur, 1);
5595  }
5596  if (ret == 0) {
5597  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FREE_FALL, (uint8_t*)&free_fall, 1);
5598  }
5599  return ret;
5600 }
5601 
5610 int32_t lsm6dsox_ff_dur_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, uint8_t *val)
5611 {
5612  lsm6dsox_wake_up_dur_t wake_up_dur;
5613  lsm6dsox_free_fall_t free_fall;
5614  int32_t ret;
5615 
5616  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_WAKE_UP_DUR, (uint8_t*)&wake_up_dur, 1);
5617  if (ret == 0) {
5618  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FREE_FALL, (uint8_t*)&free_fall, 1);
5619  *val = (wake_up_dur.ff_dur << 5) + free_fall.ff_dur;
5620  }
5621  return ret;
5622 }

5643 int32_t lsm6dsox_fifo_watermark_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t val)
5644 {
5645  lsm6dsox_fifo_ctrl1_t fifo_ctrl1;
5646  lsm6dsox_fifo_ctrl2_t fifo_ctrl2;

5652  fifo_ctrl2.wtm = (uint8_t)(( 0x0100U & val ) >> 8);

5654  }
5655  if (ret == 0) {

5743 int32_t lsm6dsox_compression_algo_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx,
5744  lsm6dsox_uncoptr_rate_t val)
5745 {
5746  lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_b_t emb_func_en_b;
5747  lsm6dsox_fifo_ctrl2_t fifo_ctrl2;
5748  int32_t ret;
5749 
5750  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
5751  if (ret == 0) {
5752  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
5753  (uint8_t*)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
5754  }
5755  if (ret == 0) {
5756  emb_func_en_b.fifo_compr_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x04U) >> 2;
5757  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
5758  (uint8_t*)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
5759  }
5760  if (ret == 0) {
5761  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
5762  }
5763  if (ret == 0) {
5764 
5765  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FIFO_CTRL2,
5766  (uint8_t*)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
5767  }
5768  if (ret == 0) {
5769  fifo_ctrl2.fifo_compr_rt_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x04U) >> 2;
5770  fifo_ctrl2.uncoptr_rate = (uint8_t)val & 0x03U;
5771  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FIFO_CTRL2,
5772  (uint8_t*)&fifo_ctrl2, 1);
5773  }
5774  return ret;
5775 }

5785 int32_t lsm6dsox_compression_algo_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx,
5786  lsm6dsox_uncoptr_rate_t *val)
5787 {

5790

5792 
5793  switch ((reg.fifo_compr_rt_en<<2) | reg.uncoptr_rate) {
5794  case LSM6DSOX_CMP_DISABLE:
5795  *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_DISABLE;
5796  break;
5797  case LSM6DSOX_CMP_ALWAYS:
5798  *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_ALWAYS;
5799  break;
5800  case LSM6DSOX_CMP_8_TO_1:
5801  *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_8_TO_1;
5802  break;
5803  case LSM6DSOX_CMP_16_TO_1:
5804  *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_16_TO_1;
5805  break;
5806  case LSM6DSOX_CMP_32_TO_1:
5807  *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_32_TO_1;
5808  break;
5809  default:
5810  *val = LSM6DSOX_CMP_DISABLE;
5811  break;
5812  }

5814 }

6376 int32_t lsm6dsox_batch_counter_threshold_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t val)
6377 {
6378  lsm6dsox_counter_bdr_reg1_t counter_bdr_reg1;
6379  lsm6dsox_counter_bdr_reg2_t counter_bdr_reg2;
6380  int32_t ret;
6381 
6382  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_COUNTER_BDR_REG1,
6383  (uint8_t*)&counter_bdr_reg1, 1);
6384  if (ret == 0) {
6385  counter_bdr_reg2.cnt_bdr_th = 0x00FFU & (uint8_t)val;
6386  counter_bdr_reg1.cnt_bdr_th = (uint8_t)(0x0700U & val) >> 8;
6387  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_COUNTER_BDR_REG1,
6388  (uint8_t*)&counter_bdr_reg1, 1);
6389  }
6390  if (ret == 0) {
6391  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_COUNTER_BDR_REG2,
6392  (uint8_t*)&counter_bdr_reg2, 1);
6393  }
6394  return ret;
6395 }

6405 int32_t lsm6dsox_batch_counter_threshold_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t *val)
6406 {

6408  lsm6dsox_counter_bdr_reg2_t counter_bdr_reg2;

6412  (uint8_t*)&counter_bdr_reg1, 1);

6414  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_COUNTER_BDR_REG2,
6415  (uint8_t*)&counter_bdr_reg2, 1);
6416 
6417  *val = ((uint16_t)counter_bdr_reg1.cnt_bdr_th << 8)
6418  + (uint16_t)counter_bdr_reg2.cnt_bdr_th;
6419  }

6438  (uint8_t*)&fifo_status1, 1);
6439  if (ret == 0) {
6440  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FIFO_STATUS2,
6441  (uint8_t*)&fifo_status2, 1);
6442  *val = ((uint16_t)fifo_status2.diff_fifo << 8) +
6443  (uint16_t)fifo_status1.diff_fifo;
6444  }
6445  return ret;
6446 }

7153 
7173 int32_t lsm6dsox_pedo_sens_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_pedo_md_t val)
7174 {
7175  lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_a_t emb_func_en_a;
7176  lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_b_t emb_func_en_b;
7177  lsm6dsox_pedo_cmd_reg_t pedo_cmd_reg;
7178  int32_t ret;
7179 
7180  ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PEDO_CMD_REG,
7181  (uint8_t*)&pedo_cmd_reg);
7182  if (ret == 0) {
7183  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
7184  }
7185  if (ret == 0) {
7186  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_A,
7187  (uint8_t*)&emb_func_en_a, 1);
7188  }
7189  if (ret == 0) {
7190  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
7191  (uint8_t*)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
7192 
7193  emb_func_en_a.pedo_en = (uint8_t)val & 0x01U;
7194  emb_func_en_b.mlc_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x02U)>>1;
7195  pedo_cmd_reg.fp_rejection_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x10U)>>4;
7196  pedo_cmd_reg.ad_det_en = ((uint8_t)val & 0x20U)>>5;
7197  }
7198  if (ret == 0) {
7199  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_A,
7200  (uint8_t*)&emb_func_en_a, 1);
7201  }
7202  if (ret == 0) {
7203  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
7204  (uint8_t*)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
7205  }
7206  if (ret == 0) {
7207  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
7208  }
7209  if (ret == 0) {
7210  ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PEDO_CMD_REG,
7211  (uint8_t*)&pedo_cmd_reg);
7212  }
7213  return ret;
7214 }
7215 
7223 int32_t lsm6dsox_pedo_sens_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, lsm6dsox_pedo_md_t *val)
7224 {
7225  lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_a_t emb_func_en_a;
7226  lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_b_t emb_func_en_b;
7227  lsm6dsox_pedo_cmd_reg_t pedo_cmd_reg;
7228  int32_t ret;
7229 
7230  ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_PEDO_CMD_REG,
7231  (uint8_t*)&pedo_cmd_reg);
7232  if (ret == 0) {
7233  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
7234  }
7235  if (ret == 0) {
7236  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_A,
7237  (uint8_t*)&emb_func_en_a, 1);
7238  }
7239  if (ret == 0) {
7240  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
7241  (uint8_t*)&emb_func_en_b, 1);
7242  }
7243  if (ret == 0) {
7244  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
7245  }
7246  switch ( (pedo_cmd_reg.ad_det_en <<5) | (pedo_cmd_reg.fp_rejection_en << 4) |
7247  (emb_func_en_b.mlc_en << 1) | emb_func_en_a.pedo_en) {
7248  case LSM6DSOX_PEDO_DISABLE:
7249  *val = LSM6DSOX_PEDO_DISABLE;
7250  break;
7251  case LSM6DSOX_PEDO_BASE_MODE:
7252  *val = LSM6DSOX_PEDO_BASE_MODE;
7253  break;
7254  case LSM6DSOX_PEDO_ADV_MODE:
7255  *val = LSM6DSOX_PEDO_ADV_MODE;
7256  break;
7257  case LSM6DSOX_FALSE_STEP_REJ:
7258  *val = LSM6DSOX_FALSE_STEP_REJ;
7259  break;
7260  case LSM6DSOX_FALSE_STEP_REJ_ADV_MODE:
7261  *val = LSM6DSOX_FALSE_STEP_REJ_ADV_MODE;
7262  break;
7263  default:
7264  *val = LSM6DSOX_PEDO_DISABLE;
7265  break;
7266  }
7267  return ret;
7268 }

8225 int32_t lsm6dsox_fsm_enable_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx,
8226  lsm6dsox_emb_fsm_enable_t *val)
8227 {
8228  int32_t ret;
8229  lsm6dsox_emb_func_en_b_t reg;
8230 
8231 
8232  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMBEDDED_FUNC_BANK);
8233  if (ret == 0) {
8234  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_ENABLE_A,
8235  (uint8_t*)&val->fsm_enable_a, 1);
8236  }
8237  if (ret == 0) {
8238  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_ENABLE_B,
8239  (uint8_t*)&val->fsm_enable_b, 1);
8240  }
8241  if (ret == 0) {
8242  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B,
8243  (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
8244  }
8245  if (ret == 0) {
8246  if ( (val->fsm_enable_a.fsm1_en |
8247  val->fsm_enable_a.fsm2_en |
8248  val->fsm_enable_a.fsm3_en |
8249  val->fsm_enable_a.fsm4_en |
8250  val->fsm_enable_a.fsm5_en |
8251  val->fsm_enable_a.fsm6_en |
8252  val->fsm_enable_a.fsm7_en |
8253  val->fsm_enable_a.fsm8_en |
8254  val->fsm_enable_b.fsm9_en |
8255  val->fsm_enable_b.fsm10_en |
8256  val->fsm_enable_b.fsm11_en |
8257  val->fsm_enable_b.fsm12_en |
8258  val->fsm_enable_b.fsm13_en |
8259  val->fsm_enable_b.fsm14_en |
8260  val->fsm_enable_b.fsm15_en |
8261  val->fsm_enable_b.fsm16_en )
8262  != PROPERTY_DISABLE){
8263  reg.fsm_en = PROPERTY_ENABLE;
8264  }
8265  else{
8266  reg.fsm_en = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
8267  }
8268 
8269  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
8270  }
8271  if (ret == 0) {
8272  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
8273  }
8274 
8275  return ret;
8276 }

8570 int32_t lsm6dsox_long_cnt_int_value_set(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t val)
8571 {
8572  int32_t ret;
8573  uint8_t add_l;
8574  uint8_t add_h;
8575 
8576  add_h = (uint8_t)( ( val & 0xFF00U ) >> 8 );
8577  add_l = (uint8_t)( val & 0x00FFU );
8578 
8579  ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_L, &add_l);
8580  if (ret == 0) {
8581  ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_write_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_H, &add_h);
8582  }
8583 
8584  return ret;
8585 }

8597 int32_t lsm6dsox_long_cnt_int_value_get(lsm6dsox_ctx_t *ctx, uint16_t *val)
8598 {
8599  int32_t ret;
8600  uint8_t add_l;
8601  uint8_t add_h;
8602 
8603  ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_L, &add_l);
8604  if (ret == 0) {
8605  ret = lsm6dsox_ln_pg_read_byte(ctx, LSM6DSOX_FSM_LC_TIMEOUT_H, &add_h);
8606  *val = add_h;
8607  *val = *val << 8;
8608  *val += add_l;
8609  }
8610 
8611  return ret;
8612 }

8722  if (ret == 0) {

8727  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_EN_B, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
8728  }
8729  if ((val != PROPERTY_DISABLE) && (ret == 0)){
8730  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_INIT_B,
8731  (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
8732  if (ret == 0) {
8733  reg.mlc_en = val;
8734  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_EMB_FUNC_INIT_B,
8735  (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
8736  }
8737  }
8738  if (ret == 0) {
8739  ret = lsm6dsox_mem_bank_set(ctx, LSM6DSOX_USER_BANK);
8740  }
8741  return ret;
8742 }

9260

9262  if (ret == 0) {
9263  ret = lsm6dsox_read_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MASTER_CONFIG, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
9264  }
9265  if (ret == 0) {
9266  reg.rst_master_regs = PROPERTY_ENABLE;
9267  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MASTER_CONFIG, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
9268  }
9269  if (ret == 0) {
9270  reg.rst_master_regs = PROPERTY_DISABLE;
9271  ret = lsm6dsox_write_reg(ctx, LSM6DSOX_MASTER_CONFIG, (uint8_t*)&reg, 1);
